                  <span class="text-gray-700">Regular equipment calibration</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-hr-accent rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Documented quality controls</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-hr-accent rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Comprehensive reporting systems</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Perth Project Examples -->
        <div class="bg-hr-dark rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-hr-accent">Recent Perth Engineering Surveyor Projects</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-hr-accent">Victoria Park-Canning Level Crossing Removal</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
                A complex infrastructure project requiring a Perth engineering surveyor with expertise in rail systems, road infrastructure, and utility coordination in an established urban environment.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-hr-accent">Lumiere Apartments, South Perth</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
                High-rise residential development requiring a Perth engineering surveyor for millimetre-precision foundation and structural surveys in a challenging riverside location.
